Assembly is a breeze, no installation tools are required and it usually takes only 1 minute to complete!

High Capacity Organization: Our Bathroom Corner Shelf Countertop saves up to 80% of desk space for your everyday needs. The higher tier spacing improves vertical space utilization, allowing for easy access to cosmetics, lotions, cleansers, perfumes and toiletries from the bathroom vanity organizer.

Multi-Situation Application: This corner shelf can be used as a skincare organizer, perfume holder organizer, bathroom countertop organizer, vanity organizer, cosmetic organizer and more. Suitable for bedroom, bathroom, dresser and kitchen, make your house neat and exquisite.

Gifts and Customer Service: The countertop organizer box is overall light luxury vintage style, it is a perfect gift for Christmas, Valentine's Day, Mother's Day, Thanksgiving, Birthday and many other festivals. If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us, we will surely solve the problem for you at the first time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Elegant and Functional
reviews.reviewText: Assembly was a breeze – the process was straightforward, and it was packaged well so the product arrived in great condition, without a single scratch.The organizer's color scheme is particularly striking. The deep olive green exudes sophistication and blends seamlessly with various decor styles. This shade of green adds a touch of elegance without overpowering the space. The gold accents complement the green perfectly, and the finish on the metal parts doesn't give the impression that it would chip off easily, suggesting durability and quality.Functionally, it offers ample space for storing and organizing a range of items, from makeup and perfumes to other bathroom essentials, without taking up too much counter space. The corner design is a smart space-saving feature, especially for smaller bathrooms or vanity areas.In terms of quality, the organizer feels sturdy and well-made. It stands stable, and the materials used appear to be of good quality, assuring me of its longevity.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for my daily use products.
reviews.reviewText: This corner storage is exactly what I needed for my toiletries. They are always scattered across my sink and I can never find what I need. This was easy to put together and the 3 tiers hold so much of the things I use daily, hair products, brushes, moisturizer etc. The curved design fits perfectly in the corner of my sink vanity and everything is neat and within reach.
